expected that beating

82
00:05:17,208 --> 00:05:20,250
the disease of aging would
bring me this kind of happiness.

83
00:05:20,333 --> 00:05:23,125
But that's something a
person can't understand

84
00:05:23,208 --> 00:05:25,583
until they embrace
a cyborg body.

85
00:05:25,666 --> 00:05:27,000
Sir, even with all our advances,

86
