232
00:12:13,333 --> 00:12:15,916
There are three elements
that comprise charisma.

233
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:19,666
As you said, there's the innate
appeal, often found in leaders.

234
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:21,791
